</action>
</testgroup>
<testgroup id = "AENBP70AA504013024">
<title>
CPP No.2 switch signal circuit check
</title>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Disconnect CPP No.2 switch and “L10” connectors connector.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Check for proper terminal connection to CPP No.2 switch and “L10” connectors.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
If connections are OK, check the following points.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Resistance of “A2” circuit: less than 1 Ω
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Resistance between “A2” circuit and ground: infinity
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Resistance between “A2” circuit terminal and each terminal at CPP No.2 switch connector: infinity
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</test1>
<question>
Are they in good condition?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to Step 5.
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Repair or replace defective wire harness.
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
